id=force-adb
name=Force ADB and Bypass Setup Wizard
version=0.1.0
versionCode=1
author=aminnur + Hermes
summary=Forces ADB/USB debugging state and disables setup wizard packages on boot for damaged-screen recovery workflows.
description=Boot-time Magisk module used after TWRP/multidisabler/data-format recovery to keep ADB reachable on a damaged-screen Samsung device.
